London-based Disc jokey Florence Otedola, aka DJ Cuppy has described Nigerian-born British boxer, Anthony Joshua, as always her Champion. She said with or without belts, Joshua will always be her Champion and even her billionaire father, Femi Otedola, can attest to this.   Saint Square records unveils recording studio     AMVCA 8 announces digital content creator’s day competition     2022 AMVCA: Rema to join Lagbaja for first-ever joint…   Posting a picture with Joshua on Twitter, she wrote: “So proud of this man! with or without belt, always my champ. Femi knows I got him any days.” She added: ” Sometimes, the greatest friendships are the ones you never expected to be in”.